hopobject.body: Whereabouts in are you from? generique viagra sandoz As disruptive as it would be I would love to see what a government where spending matched revenue looked like. I don’t dispute that the economy could not handle the stress… anyone arguing that it could can be summarily ignored. However like all bubbles or unsustainable systems the status quo will under no circumstances last. Debt to GDP can’t go to 200% as it will under present law.
